1.title: A Tragedy Strikes the Piedrahitas
1.plot: The most important social event of the year is affected by a tragedy that will mark the fate of many.

2.title: Emilia discovers Ramón's deceit
2.plot: The woman finds out that Victoria's husband has been seeing clandestinely her best friend for a long time.

3.title: Seducing the Enemy
3.plot: The young woman manages to stumble over Victoria's son and start a friendship and start her revenge plan. Martin advises Emilia to be very careful about her intentions to seduce Daniel, but she assures him that she will play a lie as long as necessary, until justice is done.

4.title: Victoria Orders to Investigate Emilia
4.plot: The woman wants to find something that incriminates the young woman who wants to win Daniel's heart. On the other hand, Emilia plans the revenge against her 'uncle Gus', a man who during her childhood was very close to her and her father, but now discovers that he was part of the group that got him in jail and meets with him to talk about business.

5.title: Adrian and Sergio's Tragedy
5.plot: Something is happening to the father of the young men, that makes them take important decisions for the future. Emilia agrees to go out with Daniel where they enjoy their first romantic date very original and wild. How will Victoria feel when she finds out that her son is interested in Emilia?

6.title: Ramon and His Allies, Between a Cross and a Sword
6.plot: As part of her revenge plan, Emilia begins to wreak havoc within the circle of confidence of Ramon Piedrahita.On the other hand, Sergio and Adrian worry about not having money to cover the expenses of their father's funeral. However, someone will take care of this and the Lozanos will be very grateful for this gesture.

7.title: Emilia Triumphs with a New Revenge
7.plot: The woman manages to invite Senator Russi's mistress to a very important evening. Sergio spies Gabriela's boyfriend and realizes that he is being unfaithful.

8.title: Emilia's agenda
8.plot: The woman hacks the video of Dr. Romero revealing recordings of private sessions of her patients where many secrets are unveiled. Martin is in charge of doing everything possible to strengthen the bond between Adrian and Emilia, after the man decided to stay in Bogota for a while and not travel to Medellin.

9.title: Martín decides to protect Emilia
9.plot: The young man doesn't want anything bad happens to his friend and installs a hidden camera in his house in order to avoid danger. Ramon continues his extramarital affair with Lina, despite his wife's warnings. In the meantime, Victoria continues to search for the suspect who holds the recordings of her most intimate secrets.

10.title: Emilia and Martin Continue with Their Agenda
10.plot: While the man offers to help Adrián and Sergio, Emilia continues gaining the confidence of the Piedrahitas.

imdb.plot outline: Emilia Rivera (whose real name is Amanda Santana) returns to her native land with the clear intention of taking revenge on the people who caused the death of her father and destroyed their family. When Amanda was a little girl, her father got arrested, being falsely accused of a crime he did not commit; he was judged and convicted. In the end, he died in jail. The same people who took away her father made sure Amanda ends up in a juvenile detention center. At the age of 18, Amanda gets the so-desired freedom. After leaving the correctional school, she soon finds out that she is the heiress of a company created by her father and that nowadays is worth a fortune. Therefore, being backed by money and having an unshakable thirst for revenge, she decides to change her identity to take revenge on all those who stole what she loved the most.
